[1]Uthamaki wa Kristo nĩũkĩte,Na ũkĩte wĩna magongonaMarĩa maiganĩire mĩĩrĩ itũ,Mũgwanja na thakame.Mwĩrĩ wa Kristo,Urĩ na hinya.Wa magongona,Mũgwanja ma thakame.[2]Kũhehenjwo kwaninire mehia,Kũnyarirwo gũkĩnina thĩna.Kũhũrwo nĩkwaiguĩthanirie andũ.Arogocwo Mwathani.[3]Mĩtunda yaninire mĩrimũ,Gũtihio gũkĩnina mahĩtia.Ruo rwake rwanĩnire rwĩtũ,Arogocwo Mwathani.[4]Kĩeha gĩake kĩaninire ciitu,Thakame ĩrĩa oirire nĩ igongona.Nĩyo yatũheire muoyo mwerũ,Arogocwo Mwathani.
